summary:
Mistral normal response format captured. Two separate endpoints used: (1) /api/trpc/message.newChat?batch=1 (tRPC mutation, application/json) and (2) /api/chat (text/event-stream, actual streaming). Body format is tRPC httpBatchStreamLink indexed format: '{index}:{json}
' per line — NOT standard SSE 'data: {json}

'.

critical_findings.format_mismatch:
APF tried standard SSE format (data: {json}

) but Mistral uses tRPC indexed format ({index}:{json}
). This is why EventStream tab showed 0 parsed events in tests #434 and #435.
